Class RatedPredictivePlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • solver.analysis.PredictivePlayer
      • solver.reachablepoints.RatedPredictivePlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPlayer
    public class RatedPredictivePlayer
extends PredictivePlayer
    Class extending a PredictivePlayer with rating capability. This includes ratings for success and cutting off enemies.
